players.name: Montassar Talbi
players.summary: Montassar Omar Talbi is a professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Ligue 1 club Lorient. Born in France, he plays for the Tunisia national team.

players.name: Yassine Meriah
players.summary: Yassine Meriah is a Tunisian professional footballer who plays as a defender for Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1 club Espérance de Tunis, whom he captains, and the Tunisia national team.

players.name: Dylan Bronn
players.summary: Dylan Daniel Mahmoud Bronn is a professional footballer who plays as a defender for Swiss Super League club Servette. Born in France, he plays for the Tunisia national team. Before becoming professional, Bronn played in the French lower leagues with Cannes, his hometown club.

players.name: Ali Maâloul

players.name: Nader Ghandri

players.name: Yan Valery

players.name: Hannibal Mejbri

players.name: Ismaël Gharbi
players.summary: Ismaël Seifallah Gharbi is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Bundesliga club FC Augsburg, on loan from Primeira Liga club Braga. Born in France and a former youth international for France and Spain, he plays for the Tunisia national team.

players.name: Ferjani Sassi

players.name: Hadj Mahmoud

players.name: Ellyes Skhiri

players.name: Elias Achouri
players.summary: Mohamed Elias Achouri is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Danish Superliga club Copenhagen. Born in Réunion, an overseas department of France, he plays for the Tunisia national team.

players.name: Elias Saad
players.summary: Elias Saad is a professional footballer who plays as a left winger for Bundesliga club FC Augsburg. Born in Germany, he plays for the Tunisia national team, having previously been a former international for the Germany national futsal team.

players.name: Sebastian Tounekti
players.summary: Sebastian Tounekti is a professional footballer who plays as a winger for Scottish Premiership club Celtic. Born in Norway, he plays for the Tunisia national team.
